<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạảyũhā ạlậbu ạl̊mubārak̊
 maṣ̊dara ạl̊ḥubĩ ạl̊ʿajīb̊
 qad̊ badẖal̊ta ạb̊naka ʿanãạ
 fid̊yaẗaⁿ ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V2]
 2- wālrũwḥa ạl̊muʿazĩy ạảẙḍaⁿạ
 qad̊ ạảʿ̊ṭaẙtahu lanā
 wah̊wa ʿur̊būnu ạl̊mīrātẖi
 wabihi kẖatam̊tanā

[V3]
 3- wafīnā yam̊kutẖu daẘmaⁿạ
 līaẘmi fidā ạl̊jasad̊
 wabihi nas̊judu laka
 yā ạảbānā lilạảbad̊

[V4]
 4- ạảyũhā ạlậbu ạl̊mubārak̊
 naḥ̊nu bimil̊ʾi ạlsũrūr̊
 sẖākirūna faḍ̊la ḥubĩk̊
 kulã ạảj̊yāli ạldũhūr̊</lyrics>
<title>ạyhạ ạlậb ạlmbạrk mṣdr ạlḥb ạlʿjyb</title>
</song>